# 1Ô∏è‚É£3Ô∏è‚É£ FAIRNESS PROTECTION

Prevents:

‚ùå Urban suppliers dominating due to proximity
‚ùå Remote suppliers unfairly penalized
‚ùå Buyers misjudging ‚Äúcheap‚Äù but high-risk bids
‚ùå Hidden logistics failures

Creates balanced geographic competition.

